# 🎬 StreamX

StreamX is a sleek and simple movie streaming website built with HTML and CSS. It provides a visually appealing interface where users can browse and watch movie trailers. Designed as a front-end project, StreamX focuses on layout design, responsive structure, and clean user experience.

## 🌟 Features

- 🎥 Hero section with eye-catching banner and featured movie
- 🔎 Intuitive layout for movies or shows
- 📱 Fully responsive design for mobile and desktop
- 🎨 Clean UI with modern styling using pure CSS

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3

## 🚀 Getting Started

